---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Left Ventricular Assist Device (LVAD) Research - Fluid Innovation Lab',
  description: 'Research on optimizing LVAD design to minimize blood damage and improve patient outcomes.',
  ignoreTitleTemplate: true,
};

const project = {
  title: 'Left Ventricular Assist Device (LVAD) Research',
  summary: 'Research on optimizing LVAD design to minimize blood damage and improve patient outcomes.',
  image: '/images/projects/1.png',
  additionalImages: [
    {
      src: '/images/projects/2.png',
      caption: 'Design optimization to reduce blood damage'
    },
    {
      src: '/images/projects/3.png',
      caption: 'Parametric LVAD model'
    }
  ],
  content: `
Left Ventricular Assist Device (LVAD) is an effective treatment for end-stage heart failure patients. However, severe complications, including thrombosis, stroke, and bleeding, are common. Past studies have shown that the blood damage associated with the supraphysiologic shear stress in the device is the cause of those complications. The mechanical forces generated by the rotating components destroy blood cells, leading to hemolysis, and activate platelets, causing thrombus formation. It is crucial to optimize the LVAD design to achieve minimal blood damage. In this work, we first designed a parametric centrifugal LVAD model and built a computational framework to assess blood damage. Subsequently, preliminary design optimization was carried out. Results from different models have shown significant improvement in performance after optimization.
  `
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 mx-auto lg:px-8 lg:py-20 max-w-7xl">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 font-heading bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-teal-400">
        {project.title}
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted dark:text-slate-400">
        {project.summary}
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Main Image -->
      <div class="mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <img
          src={project.image}
          alt={project.title}
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert mx-auto">
        <p class="whitespace-pre-line">{project.content}</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Additional Images -->
      <div class="mt-16">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          {project.additionalImages.map((img, index) => (
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105">
              <img
                src={img.src}
                alt={`${project.title} - Visualization ${index + 2}`}
                class="w-full h-auto"
              />
              <div class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
                <p class="text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-medium">{img.caption}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout> 